    "sub_sektor": "Farm Products",
    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Sreeya Sewu Indonesia Tbk engages in breeding to produce commercial chickens, chicken slaughter, and integrated chicken processing with cold storage in Indonesia. It operates through Poultry Feeds; Breeder and Farm; and Dressed Chicken and Frozen Foods segments. The company offers broiler, layer, breeder, concentrate, quail, and bird feed; and other type of feeds in the form of flour, pellet, crumble, and expander. It also operates day old chick (DOC) breeding and hatchery farms, which are cultivated by broiler and layer farmers to produce live birds; and slaughterhouses that produce live birds from DOC broilers. In addition, the company offers dressed chicken products to various supermarkets, hypermarkets, restaurants, café, and other outlets; and frozen food, including processed chicken, chicken nuggets, sausages, corned and meatballs under the Royal, Belfoods, and Uenakk brand names. Further, it is involved in the food processing industry; and distribution and trading of poultry equipment, raw materials, feedmill, and other products. The company was formerly known as PT Sierad Produce Tbk and changed its name to PT Sreeya Sewu Indonesia Tbk in September 2020. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Sreeya Sewu Indonesia Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Great Giant Pineapple.",
